summary:
Can we talk about this moment in Episode 2? Look at the paths the two of
 them take, to get to the gates of the convent....
caption: Can we talk about this moment in Episode 2? Look at the paths the two of them take, to get to the gates of the convent. Aziraphale makes sure that he follows the landscaped path set out for them, and Crowley deliberately goes out of his way to just cut straight across the grass. It’s a subtle moment, but damn if it doesn’t speak to their characters.
